725629f-d.title: Queens: 73rd Avenue - 195th Street
725629f-d.text:
73rd Avenue, south side, at 195th Street, showing the Ditmars
Stoothoff farmhouse of 1860. Other owners were Remsen in 1873
and Mrs Powell in 1896.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1922

725630f-b.title: Queens: 73rd Avenue - 195th Street
725630f-b.text:

farmhouse and barn. Owners were: Ditmars Stoothoff-1860;
Remsen-1873; Mrs. Powell-1896. 73rd Avenue is the former
Black Stump Road.
